{"tid":831743,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"復仇者聯盟夠唔夠佢地打","createTime":"2018-09-22T08:13:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-22T14:01:28.000Z","uid":161790,"like":54,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"119c55a9a3527daaad46500f37184dd760a63539","tid":831743,"uid":161790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T08:13:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/22/154541_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F22%2F154541_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=2b94095a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個個都係小丑級數<br />\n大咪捉iron man老婆 自動收皮<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/22/155554_fa63fcaedf609188d03a584e59adaa5b.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F22%2F155554_fa63fcaedf609188d03a584e59adaa5b.JPG&h=48e71fe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nHulk同大傻打 死路一條<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/22/155713_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F22%2F155713_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=44b57126&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n女巫黑寡婦會比沙蜢屈射龍門冇哂錢 賣去火坑<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/22/155956_fa63fcaedf609188d03a584e59adaa5b.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F22%2F155956_fa63fcaedf609188d03a584e59adaa5b.JPG&h=d18b5850&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n駱駝吹雞 美國隊長死梗<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/22/160236_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F22%2F160236_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=1e722c35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有基哥會自動反骨出賣 令復仇者聯盟解散冇backup<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/22/160605_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F22%2F160605_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=8a02da37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n高義潛伏黑豹身邊扮狗 攞哂啲科技 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/22/161125_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F22%2F161125_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=37222b68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n奸人堅會用奸計 離間隊友<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/22/161251_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F22%2F161251_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=39e4ec6b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bf175a581098de3a52d89e7544c22f5b308f66d3","tid":831743,"uid":1354,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T08:15:08.000Z","msg":"好無聊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c89702fa88441382ec7584f77cefc03fac6c52a7","tid":831743,"uid":34023,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"bf175a581098de3a52d89e7544c22f5b308f66d3","tid":831743,"uid":1354,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T08:15:08.000Z","msg":"好無聊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T08:17:56.000Z","msg":"都有心機嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc5a300d88fa480a7d0807bb0970b243674cc9ee","tid":831743,"uid":1354,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c89702fa88441382ec7584f77cefc03fac6c52a7","tid":831743,"uid":34023,"like":6,"dislike":0,"scor